{"id":505168,"date":[{"year":1970,"month":9,"day":21}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"风雷激","column":"庆祝中华人民共和国成立二十一周年(1949—1970)","genre":"","count":"293","ytitle":"","mtitle":"走过电灌渠","ftitle":"","authors":["傅歆"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"奉贤县　傅歆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过电灌渠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"倾听流水声:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哗啦啦，哗啦啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水过处秧苗青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱天夺来好年成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电灌水呵水流长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老队长渠旁说话响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句记心上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不能忘!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎能忘?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万恶旧社会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人旱天田里忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜踏水车到天亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏断脊骨梁啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依旧债满筐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记得土改分田地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"单干少力量。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风车呼呼转呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河水慢慢淌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱天还是秧苗黄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经历了互助组、合作社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社力量强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"电力灌溉斗天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天旱地不旱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收万年长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放眼全球多打粮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲风云担肩上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一粒稻谷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一颗子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"消灭帝修反野心狼!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席亲手开大道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里风云万里涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在公社大路上啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红太阳永远当头照!"}]}